  "prompt": "How do I change One Plus 3 ringtone?",
  "response": "To change the ringtone on your OnePlus 3, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Open Settings**: Unlock your OnePlus 3 and navigate to the home screen. Tap on the \"Settings\" app, which is represented by a gear icon.\n\n2. **Sound & Vibration**: Scroll down and tap on \"Sound & Vibration.\"\n\n3. **Ringtone**: In the \"Sound & Vibration\" menu, tap on \"Ringtone.\"\n\n4. **Select a Ringtone**: You will see a list of available ringtones. Tap on the one you want to use. You can also tap on \"Add from device storage\" to select a custom ringtone from your phone's storage.\n\n5. **Confirm Selection**: After selecting a ringtone, tap \"OK\" or \"Save\" to confirm your choice.\n\nYour OnePlus 3 should now use the newly selected ringtone for incoming calls.",
